(screaming)

286
00:13:15,862 --> 00:13:27,273
♪

287
00:13:27,273 --> 00:13:31,444
We put up a desperate
battle, but...

288
00:13:31,444 --> 00:13:34,647
we were no match for
their cunning tactics.

289
00:13:34,647 --> 00:14:12,685
♪

290
00:14:12,685 --> 00:14:16,389
The defeated must
always obey the victors.

291
00:14:16,389 --> 00:14:19,992
That's how we became followers
of our enemy, Gray Wolf.

292
00:14:19,992 --> 00:14:21,561
He acknowledged our strength

293
00:14:21,561 --> 00:14:24,731
and gave us reign
over this territory.

294
00:14:24,731 --> 00:14:27,066
‐Unforgivable!
‐Hm?

295
00:14:27,066 --> 00:14:30,603
Gray Wolf taking advantage
of wounded warriors.

296
00:14:30,603 --> 00:14:32,372
Where's the honor in that?

297
00:14:32,372 --> 00:14:34,807
The reality is that
a defeat is a defeat,

298
00:14:34,807 --> 00:14:37,343
no matter what
the circumstances.

299
00:14:37,343 --> 00:14:38,344
But‐‐

300
00:14:38,344 --> 00:14:40,113
That is the warrior's rule.

301
00:14:40,113 --> 00:14:42,215
It is our custom.

302
00:14:42,215 --> 00:14:43,249
(groaning)

303
00:14:43,249 --> 00:14:44,384
Huh?

304
00:14:44,384 --> 00:14:46,085
Centaur, we have to get
you to the Fountain.

305
00:14:46,085 --> 00:14:47,754
I've been hurt worse.

306
00:14:47,754 --> 00:14:50,123
‐You should see to your friends.
‐Huh?

307
00:14:50,123 --> 00:14:52,558
♪

308
00:14:52,558 --> 00:14:53,993
I'm sorry.

309
00:14:53,993 --> 00:14:56,996
♪

310
00:14:56,996 --> 00:14:58,598
(explosion)

311
00:14:58,598 --> 00:15:00,199
(exclaims)

312
00:15:00,199 --> 00:15:01,300
Huh?

313
00:15:01,300 --> 00:15:03,136
(evil cackle)

314
00:15:03,136 --> 00:15:04,904
♪

315
00:15:08,508 --> 00:15:10,877
You back again, Salamander?

316
00:15:10,877 --> 00:15:13,579
I've had it up to here
with this honor stuff.

317
00:15:13,579 --> 00:15:15,782
We've got ya this time, kid.

318
00:15:15,782 --> 00:15:19,051
You're not gonna cause
Moo any more trouble.

319
00:15:19,051 --> 00:15:22,255
You're finished.

320
00:15:22,255 --> 00:15:23,656
You.

321
00:15:23,656 --> 00:15:26,492
You defy the rules
of the warrior.

322
00:15:26,492 --> 00:15:28,194
Whatever it takes to win.

323
00:15:28,194 --> 00:15:31,030
That's the only rule
we've got, Centaur.

324
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:33,699
♪

325
00:15:33,699 --> 00:15:34,834
Leave them to me.

326
00:15:34,834 --> 00:15:35,802
Huh?

327
00:15:35,802 --> 00:15:37,537
‐Centaur.
‐Genki.

328
00:15:37,537 --> 00:15:39,705
Go now, save your friends.

329
00:15:39,705 --> 00:15:40,873
Uh...

330
00:15:40,873 --> 00:15:42,308
Go.

331
00:15:42,308 --> 00:15:43,576
Right.

332
00:15:43,576 --> 00:15:55,321
♪

333
00:15:55,321 --> 00:15:58,357
(sounds of struggle)

334
00:15:58,357 --> 00:16:07,033
♪

335
00:16:07,033 --> 00:16:09,101
I'll blame your
defeat on the kid.

336
00:16:09,101 --> 00:16:11,170
Gray Wolf will never know.

337
00:16:11,170 --> 00:16:16,676
♪

338
00:16:16,676 --> 00:16:19,312
(blasts)

339
00:16:19,312 --> 00:16:25,218
♪

340
00:16:25,218 --> 00:16:27,420
It seems, Captain Salamander,

341
00:16:27,420 --> 00:16:28,888
you don't learn.

342
00:16:28,888 --> 00:16:31,257
You will never defeat me.

343
00:16:31,257 --> 00:16:39,232
♪

344
00:16:39,232 --> 00:16:41,067
(grunting)

345
00:16:41,067 --> 00:16:43,035
Holly, is everyone all right?

346
00:16:43,035 --> 00:16:45,204
Yep, we're fine, Genki.

347
00:16:45,204 --> 00:16:46,772
Great.

348
00:16:46,772 --> 00:16:48,274
'K.

349
00:16:48,274 --> 00:16:54,046
♪

350
00:16:54,046 --> 00:16:55,548
Huh?

351
00:16:55,548 --> 00:17:01,587
♪

352
00:17:01,587 --> 00:17:04,657
Hey, you two are okay.

353
00:17:04,657 --> 00:17:06,792
Hm.

354
00:17:06,792 --> 00:17:08,761
‐Ready?
‐Yeah.

355
00:17:08,761 --> 00:17:14,033
♪

356
00:17:14,033 --> 00:17:16,002
Huh?

357
00:17:16,002 --> 00:17:21,908
♪

358
00:17:21,908 --> 00:17:25,878
I was beginning to wonder
when you two would get here.

359
00:17:25,878 --> 00:17:28,381
We had a few
weighty problems.

360
00:17:28,381 --> 00:17:29,849
But showed those
Salamander troops

361
00:17:29,849 --> 00:17:32,118
a thing or two
about warriors.

362
00:17:32,118 --> 00:17:33,753
(blades clang)

363
00:17:33,753 --> 00:17:35,855
♪

364
00:17:35,855 --> 00:17:37,990
(whimpering)

365
00:17:37,990 --> 00:17:41,294
(rumbling)

366
00:17:41,294 --> 00:17:42,929
Oh!

367
00:17:42,929 --> 00:17:44,130
Genki!

368
00:17:44,130 --> 00:17:45,665
‐Thank you.
‐Mocchi!

369
00:17:45,665 --> 00:17:47,400
Awesome!

370
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:50,636
♪

371
00:17:50,636 --> 00:17:52,338
Heads up, guys!

372
00:17:52,338 --> 00:17:57,143
♪

373
00:17:57,143 --> 00:17:58,644
Lightning!

374
00:17:58,644 --> 00:17:59,712
Huh?

375
00:17:59,712 --> 00:18:01,280
What now?

376
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:03,516
♪

377
00:18:03,516 --> 00:18:05,751
Let's get 'em!

378
00:18:05,751 --> 00:18:07,553
Chi!

379
00:18:07,553 --> 00:18:24,704
♪

380
00:18:24,704 --> 00:18:26,639
I am Centaur!

381
00:18:26,639 --> 00:18:31,611
♪

382
00:18:31,611 --> 00:18:35,014
You can be sure we'll
meet again, Centaur!

383
00:18:35,014 --> 00:18:37,750
Retreat!

384
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:39,986
(celebrating)

385
00:18:39,986 --> 00:18:42,154
(laughter)

386
00:18:42,154 --> 00:18:47,493
♪

387
00:18:47,493 --> 00:18:49,295
Uh...

388
00:18:49,295 --> 00:18:51,297
Goodbye.

389
00:18:51,297 --> 00:19:00,506
♪

390
00:19:00,506 --> 00:19:03,075
We pointed our
swords at allies.

391
00:19:03,075 --> 00:19:06,178
We will receive retribution.

392
00:19:06,178 --> 00:19:07,913
♪

393
00:19:07,913 --> 00:19:11,517
You mean, the Salamander
troops will be back again?

394
00:19:11,517 --> 00:19:12,551
Mm‐hm.

395
00:19:12,551 --> 00:19:14,286
But they don't fight fair.

396
00:19:14,286 --> 00:19:16,656
I'll stay here
and fight with you.

397
00:19:16,656 --> 00:19:17,823
Chi!

398
00:19:17,823 --> 00:19:20,026
(Tiger growls)

399
00:19:20,026 --> 00:19:22,595
You must move on now.

400
00:19:22,595 --> 00:19:24,764
We can take care of them.

401
00:19:24,764 --> 00:19:27,066
But we can help you.

402
00:19:27,066 --> 00:19:28,300
Go.

403
00:19:28,300 --> 00:19:29,301
Huh?

404
00:19:29,301 --> 00:19:31,070
You are a true warrior.

405
00:19:31,070 --> 00:19:33,939
You possess a soul and
eyes that are clear.

406
00:19:33,939 --> 00:19:36,709
You have a quest you
must fulfill, Genki,

407
00:19:36,709 --> 00:19:39,745
so you must go now.

408
00:19:39,745 --> 00:19:42,715
We'll meet again, won't we?

409
00:19:42,715 --> 00:19:45,151
That is not ours to say.

410
00:19:45,151 --> 00:19:46,886
Let us go.

411
00:19:46,886 --> 00:19:51,023
♪

412
00:19:51,023 --> 00:19:52,425
Centaur!

413
00:19:52,425 --> 00:19:54,326
We're not done yet!

414
00:19:54,326 --> 00:19:57,329
I challenge you
to a rematch!

415
00:19:57,329 --> 00:20:09,775
♪

416
00:20:09,775 --> 00:20:11,944
(sniffling)

417
00:20:11,944 --> 00:20:14,146
♪

418
00:20:14,146 --> 00:20:15,815
Are you okay?

419
00:20:15,815 --> 00:20:23,289
♪

420
00:20:23,289 --> 00:20:24,857
Yeah!

421
00:20:24,857 --> 00:20:27,793
Let's find the Phoenix.

422
00:20:27,793 --> 00:20:30,796
Down with Moo, goodies rule!

423
00:20:30,796 --> 00:20:32,698
Okay!

424
00:20:32,698 --> 00:20:46,779
♪

425
00:20:46,779 --> 00:20:48,013
♪ Monsters ♪

426
00:20:48,013 --> 00:20:49,515
♪ Monsters rule ♪

427
00:20:49,515 --> 00:21:14,140
♪

428
00:21:14,140 --> 00:21:16,008
♪ Monsters rule ♪

